lang=EN-US> 14 000 000<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P 
style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 48pt; mso-char-indent-count: 4.0"><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">贷：应付职工薪酬――辞退福利<SPAN 
lang=EN-US> 14 000 000<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">七、关于其他长期职工福利的确认和计量<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">其他长期职工福利，是指除短期薪酬、离职后福利和辞退福利以外的其他所有职工福利。其他长期职工福利包括长期带薪缺勤、其他长期服务福利、长期残疾福利、长期利润分享计划和长期奖金计划等。<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">企业向职工提供的其他长期职工福利，符合设定提存计划条件的，应当按照设定提存计划的有关规定进行会计处理。企业向职工提供的其他长期职工福利，符合设定受益计划条件的，企业应当按照设定受益计划的有关规定，确认和计量其他长期职工福利净负债或净资产。在报告期末，企业应当将其他长期职工福利产生的职工薪酬成本确认为下列组成部分：<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">1. 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">服务成本。<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">2. 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">其他长期职工福利净负债或净资产的利息净额。<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">3. 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">重新计量其他长期职工福利净负债或净资产所产生的变动。<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">为了简化相关会计处理，上述项目的总净额应计入当期损益或相关资产成本。<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">长期残疾福利水平取决于职工提供服务期间长短的，企业应在职工提供服务的期间确认应付<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">长期残疾福利义务，计量时应当考虑长期残疾福利支付的可能性和预期支付的期限；与职工提供服务期间长短无关的，企业应当在导致职工长期残疾的事件发生的当期确认应付长期残疾福利义务。<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">八、关于职工薪酬的披露<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">在资产负债表中，企业应当根据应支付的职工薪酬负债流动性，对职工薪酬负债按照流动和非流动进行分类列报。短期薪酬、离职后福利中的设定提存计划负债、其他长期职工福利中的符合设定提存计划条件的负债、辞退福利中将于资产负债表日后十二个月内支付的部分应当在资产负债表的流动负债项下“应付职工薪酬”项目中列示。辞退福利中将于资产负债表日起十二个月之后支付的部分、离职后福利中设定受益计划净负债、其他长期职工福利中符合设定受益计划条件的净负债应当在资产负债表的非流动负债项下单独列示。<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN 
style="mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">对于重新计量设定受益计划净负债或净资产所产生的变动，企业如在权益范围内转移这些在其他综合收益中确认的金额，应当在所有者权益变动表“（四）所有者权益内部结转”项下“<SPAN 
lang=EN-US>3. </SPAN>盈余公积弥补亏损”和“<SPAN lang=EN-US>4. </SPAN>其他”项目之间增设“<SPAN 
lang=EN-US>4. </SPAN>结转重新计量设定受益计划净负债或净资产所产生的变动”项目（“其他”项目序号顺延）加以列示。<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN 
